    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Methionyl r-Green Mussel Oligopeptide-1) is a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from r-Green Mussel Oligopeptide-1 with the initiation code for methionine. The fusion peptide contains 63 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
    ],
